name: Mei Triptych #1
description:
Mei Triptych is derived from a special edition of Mei. In this edition, the color palette features large drifts of snow on branches of Mei and is only present in snowy weather. The landscape was made continuously across the three pieces and is generated from a piece of cusmomized code in one run.

Resolution: 6200x4000
Format: PNG
Code: p5js
